CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, May 26, 1956, pg. 18 reads: "In Class - Mrs. Eunice Cook, right, instructs a Red Cross class in duties of nurses aide. Left to right: Mrs. Estelle Frazier, Mrs. Bertha Reddick and MRs. Lilly Carrington. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Estelle Frazier holding pitcher, Bertha Reddick, Lilly Carrington lying in bed, and nurse Eunice Cook wearing Red Cross uniform demonstrating patient care
